name: Whoooooo!!!!
description:
At Vierge we love our animals and mainly our owls.. These beautiful creatures represent an higher status and we wear them proud.. 

Comes in all kinds of colors and shapes an designs..


The owl is sacred to the Greek goddess of learning, Athena and is even depicted as a symbol of status, intelligence and of course, wealth.

Custom orders contact me at viergeaccessories@hotmail.com or hit the contact link

name: Big Man
description:
I love these earrings with a sleek straight ponytail or show them off with a fro/Mohawk or even a short cut...

These are attention grabbers so please don't be alarm when random people began to approach you about these earrings.

name: "I Do Nails
description:
This is for all the nail techs out there... 

Walk around and let it be known what your profession is...

If you love the craft of nails as much as I do then this piece would be amazing...

Advertise yourself

Also comes in "I DO HAIR" and "I DO MAKEUP"

description:
This bracelet is a constant reminder, to always believe in yourself..

Comes in any colors and styles...
